#   - Modified: [YYYY-MM-DD - what changed]
#
# # Purpose & Function
#
# Purpose: Define and maintain consistent coding styles across editors/IDEs
#
# Core Design: Universal formatting rules that all editors respect
#
# Key Features:
#
#   - Indent style (spaces vs tabs) and size
#   - Line ending normalization (LF for Linux-first)
#   - Character encoding (UTF-8)
#   - Trailing whitespace handling
#   - Final newline enforcement
#
# # Health Scoring
#
# Configuration Impact: Inconsistent formatting creates merge conflicts and
# reduces code readability
#
# Validation Behavior:
